name: CHRISTMAS PRE-ORDER NOV 1 to DEC 15, 2013
description:
CHRISTMAS PRE-ORDER BEFORE DEC. 15TH, 2013

When you order 2 or more photo boxes before Dec. 15th, you save!!!

Your photos, your memories.  A sweet, unique and personal gift idea.  Custom photo effects with 3D accent. 

*This SALE does not apply to the Through the Viewfinder (TTV) or Mini-Polaroid Photo Boxes*

Measurements:

Width: 9 ¾ "
Height: 9 ¾ "

Theme ideas; Friends, Family, Fashion, Wedding, Birthday, Photography, Document Travels, Loves, Children - Boys & Girls, New Baby, Food, the list can go on and on...

Choose a Black or White (or same color) Ikea Ribba Frame that can be hung or stand on its own against a wall.

*NOTE* WHITE SOLD OUT UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE
